column20:
Enter your job description in this box here. It doesn't matter what you put here as long as it's some sort of text.

I can even add text on newlines with no problem.

Or what about bullet points:
• No problem!
• HTML
• CSS
• C++
• Excel
• UI Design
• Statistics

And don't worry about upper or lower case either. Or weirdly formatted text. The parser can handle it all.

HTML, html, HtMl, H/T//mL is all the same!
